      "content": "thanks. i'll try the antihistamine now. do u think i need a doctor right away though? im kinda worried it might be getting a bit harder to catch my breath but i dont want to go to the emergency room if it's just allergies. like, is there something else i can do at home to make the wheezing stop faster?",
